@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rsoqye(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.38) + (v1 + 0.06 * tmp + 0.87)))
    v2 = ((0.03 / wp.exp(tmp + 0.06)) / tmp)
    v2 = wp.abs(0.92)
    v1 = v2
    v2 = wp.abs(0.03)
    data[tid] = v0
